   186	            # When ref ≈ 0, |actual-ref|/|ref| → ∞ even for small |actual|.
   187	            # Fallback: |error| <= tolerance * max(|ref|, 1.0) treats near-zero like regular.
   188	            if abs(expected) < 1e-6:
