     1	# Under-resolved teaching run for lid_driven_cavity.
     2	#
     3	# Pedagogical construction: a coarse 32x32 grid on the [0,1]² cavity
     4	# resolves the primary vortex poorly near the bottom-left corner where
     5	# u_x at y=0.0625 is small and sensitive to discretization. Published
     6	# grid-refinement studies (e.g., Ghia 1982 Tab III) show ~20-35%
     7	# underestimate on this probe at 32² vs the 129² reference.
     8	#
     9	# This fixture's value (-0.029) is a typical 32² outcome, reproducing
    10	# the magnitude of the error without pretending to be a specific real run.
